sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Route as ds-pipeline Route<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS Reencrypt
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as Minio/S3<br/>9000/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Tekton as Tekton API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as Scheduled Workflow Controller
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard

    Note over User,API: Flow 1: User Submits Pipeline via API
    User->>Router: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    Router->>Route: Forward to Route<br/>TLS termination
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443 Reencrypt<br/>Service CA cert
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate Bearer Token<br/>OpenShift OAuth
    OAuth->>API: HTTP/8888<br/>Token verified (localhost)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline definition<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>Auth: DB credentials
    API->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>HTTP(S)/9000 or 443<br/>Auth: S3 credentials
    API->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>OAuth: Response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Router: Forward response
    Router-->>User: JSON response

    Note over PA,Tekton: Flow 2: Persistence Agent Syncs Run Status
    loop Every 2 seconds
        PA->>Tekton: Watch PipelineRuns<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Tekton-->>PA: PipelineRun status changes
        PA->>API: Update run status<br/>HTTP/8888 TLS internal<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        API->>DB: Update run metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>Auth: DB credentials
        PA->>S3: Archive logs/artifacts<br/>HTTP(S)/9000 or 443<br/>Auth: S3 credentials
    end

    Note over SWC,Tekton: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Creates Pipeline Run
    SWC->>SWC: Cron trigger fires
    SWC->>Tekton: Check existing runs<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    SWC->>API: Create scheduled run<br/>HTTP/8888 TLS internal<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    API->>Tekton: Create PipelineRun<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: pipeline-runner SA Token

    Note over Dashboard,MLMD: Flow 4: MLMD Lineage Tracking (Optional)
    Dashboard->>Envoy: Query artifact lineage<br/>gRPC/9090<br/>Auth: Network Policy
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward gRPC request<br/>gRPC/8080<br/>Auth: None (internal)
    MLMD->>DB: Query metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>Auth: DB credentials
    MLMD-->>Envoy: Artifact metadata
    Envoy-->>Dashboard: gRPC response

    Note over PA,MLMD: MLMD Writer Updates Lineage
    PA->>MLMD: Write execution metadata<br/>gRPC/8080<br/>Auth: None (internal)
    MLMD->>DB: Store lineage<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>Auth: DB credentials
